title: Presidential Nomination sent to the Senate, 7-24-09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




July 24, 2009

 



Presidential Nomination sent to the Senate, 7-24-09




 THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secretary  ______________________________________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                                                                July 24, 2009  NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:  Dennis F. Hightower, of the District of Columbia, to be Deputy Secretary of Commerce, vice John J. Sullivan, resigned.
